As it is a technical field, one has to be updated because the technology changes often. It is my responsibility to learn and adopt the new technology. It would be profitable for me as well as for my companyPROFESSIONAL SUMMARYHaving 5+ years of experience in the field of IT, in which 3+ years of experience in providing Workday Technical Development in Workday Support and Enhancement Project.
